At 07h00 this morning, Netcare 911 paramedics responded to a smallholding in the Randburg area for a shooting incident. Reports from the scene indicate that several gunmen entered the premises of a popular actress, shots were fired and she sustained two serious gunshot wounds.The exact detail to the incident and preceding events will however remain a subject for police comment.&nbsp;The Netcare 911 Advanced Life Support paramedics and her team arrived at the scene and found the actress to be in a serious but stable condition. The patient was treated at the scene and then transported to a specialised hospital under the constant care of an Advanced Life Support paramedic.